HabitRPG,is,a,habit,building,game,that,treats,a,user,s,life,like,a,Role,Playing,Game,Players,can,use,the,site,to,track,daily,habits,Players,are,penalized,for,indulging,bad,habits,and,rewarded,for,completing,productive,tasks,The,HabitRPG,provides,developer,access,to,the,platform,through,an,API,supporting,HTTP,POST,PUT,and,DELETE,calls,The,API,can,return,site,and,user,data,as,well,as,create,or,edit,tasks